<p>
  You can view all of the jobs entered from the <b><a href="/jobs">Jobs > View Jobs</a></b> side
  menu option.  From there, you can sort the jobs by any column.  You can select how many jobs show
  up on the page at one time, export the job list to CSV or Excel, and search for anything related to specific jobs.
</p>
